    %section
        %h2.s4 A new, rolling QA process
        %p We implemented a rolling QA process to help lessen the QA load at the end. Initially, I was a little worried that this would mean double work for the design team. But it ended up keeping the QA load to a consistent, manageable level and allowed the teams to work concurrently and meet the deadline. This will definitely be a process that I use on future projects.
